            "tab_1_heading": "Description",
            "tab_1_content_type": "text",
            "tab_1_text": "<p>AminoLean Hydration + Recovery is recovery for body and mind. After you train, your body needs to rehydrate and rebuild while your mind needs to reset, and most recovery products only handle half the job. This one covers both: hydrating electrolytes and 5g of vegan amino acids refuel and repair the body, while nootropic mushrooms help sharpen focus and clear the post-workout fog. It's all clean, naturally flavored, and free of sugar, caffeine, and anything you don't need. Real ingredients, built to recover all of you.</p>",
