            "tab_3_heading": "Directions",
            "tab_3_content_type": "text",
            "tab_3_text": "<p>Mix 1 scoops of AminoLean Recovery in 8-10 oz of cold water anytime throughout the day.</p><p><strong>RECOMMENDED USE: </strong></p><p><strong>For Anytime Energy & EAA's:</strong> Take 1 or more servings first thing in the morning and/or between meals.</p><p><strong>For Recovery & EAA's: Take 1-2 servings after training and/or between meals.</strong></p><p><strong>Do not exceed more than 6 scoops (3 servings) in a 4 hour period and do not exceed more than 8 scoops (4 servings) in a 24 hour period.</strong></p>",
